## 1.0 Requirements

### 1.1 Hardware

- Raspberry Pi Zero 2W
- Pimoroni HyperPixel Round display (480×480)
- ELM327 OBD-II adapter (Bluetooth SPP)

### 1.2 Software

- Python 3.9+
- git
- curl

